### 1. Send a Message to the AI Chat Assistant
# Requires a valid Supabase JWT for an authenticated user.
# Provide a valid `jam3iyyaId` to test the dynamic circle context injection.

POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jam3iyyaId": "1e61e679-8859-4329-a8cc-7c4a9520446f",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hello! When is my turn to receive the payout, and how much will I get?"
    }
  ]
}
